<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">答問</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">答向鑑瑩問（二則）</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="221"/>
<pb ed="TX" xml:id="TX26.0017.0480a" n="0480a"/>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">答日僧荻原虛問（四則）</cb:mulu><head>答日僧荻原虛問<note place="inline">四則</note></head>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a02"/><cb:dialog type="qa"><sp cb:type="question"><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0201" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">問一：中國佛教現狀如何？</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a03"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0301" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">問二：儒佛關係如何？</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a04"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0401" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">問三：廬山高僧何在？</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a05"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0501" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">問四：大林何宗及師信何宗？</p></sp>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a06"/><sp cb:type="answer"><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0601" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em">答一：新陳代謝復興中。</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a07"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0701" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em">答二：明月清風過太空。</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a08"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0801" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em">答三：雲自去來山不動。</p>
<lb ed="TX" n="0480a09"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0480a0901" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em">答四：又看天地闢鴻濛。</p></sp></cb:dialog><byline cb:type="other">（見正信四卷十四期）</byline></cb:div>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>